abstract.text: Internet Money Magic

inlineContent.text: MoneyKit for iOS is a quick and secure way to link bank accounts from within your iOS app. The drop-in framework handles connecting to a financial institution in your app (credential validation, multi-factor authentication, error handling, etc.) without passing sensitive information to your server.
